      • bogoSort

        public static void bogoSort(Shape[] shapes,
                            java.lang.String compareType)
        Calls the appropriate bogosort method based on compare type. Bogosort works by continually shuffling the array until it is shuffled into a sorted state. AKA - Stupid Sort
        Parameters:
        shapes - - Array of shapes to be sorted.
        compareType - - A char representing the attribute to be compared: 'h' for height, 'v' for volume, 'a' for base area.
